<title>Case Object</title>

In logic, a <logiccolor>Case</logiccolor> object facilitates the management of CSPro's case-based data.

<subheader>Functionality</subheader>

A Case object is a CSPro logic object that allows the following functions to be called via <link object_dot_notation.csdoc>dot notation</link>:

